---
Source:
  - Title: Book of Serenity
    Translator: Thomas Cleary
    ISBN: 0-940262-25-8
    Page: 364
By: Fojian
---
The seamless monument -- it's not a shadow;
Vastly empty, at once enter the realm of true suchness.
The diamond eye's lightning courses;
Vague and dark, the mark on the head isn't seen.
